dc_description_s: This data represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Sheboygan County, Wisconsin in 2019. [The current control point on the surface of the earth and its associated current coordinate value, generally determined by a surveying process and used to define an extremity of a boundary.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most recent data for this county, please visit: http://data-shebco.opendata.arcgis.com/
